 - skip any items when first checking the feed - default: true (set to false for debugging)\n\n## Notes, Plans, etc.\n\nCurrently only handles one RSS feed -- I might work on fixing that next.\n\n","maintainers":[{"name":"larcher","email":"larcher@spoon.cx"}],"time":{"modified":"2015-07-13T14:53:35.322Z","created":"2015-07-13T14:53:35.322Z","0.0.1":"2015-07-13T14:53:35.322Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/larcher/hubot-rss-alerts","keywords":["hubot","rss"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git://github.com/larcher/hubot-rss-alerts.git"},"author":{"name":"Larry Archer","email":"larcher@spoon.cx"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/larcher/hubot-rss-alerts/issues"},"readmeFilename":"README.md"}
